OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FWindy this
OL,6,Fevening with some sunny spells, but
OL,7,Falso isolated showers, mainly in the
OL,8,Fnorth of the region. Remaining windy
OL,9,Fovernight with thickening cloud and
OL,10,Fscattered showers, although some clear
OL,11,Fspells remain possible, mainly in the
OL,12,Feast.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSaturday:FOften cloudy to start with
OL,15,Fscattered showers, but sunny spells
OL,16,Fdeveloping and showers becoming more
OL,17,Fisolated, dying out later. Still windy
OL,18,Fhowever, and feeling cool.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
