OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:
OL,6,FGenerally dry with plenty of fine,
OL,7,Fbright weather expected. Winds easing
OL,8,Fby Sunday and remaining fairly light
OL,9,Fon Monday and Tuesday. Turning
OL,10,Fslightly warmer.
